{"tid":2068560,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人去過支那啲長髮村？","createTime":"2020-06-17T18:57:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T23:43:30.000Z","uid":10566,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"19777e563eb53478fbedd157be2ebb354315d840","tid":2068560,"uid":10566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T18:57:59.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n細個嗰陣去啲文化交流團<br />\n去咗條長髮村 睇佢哋表演梳頭<br />\n佢哋啲頭髮真係好撚長 <br />\n但原來佢哋唔用洗頭水同會用洗米水護髮<br />\n聽完冇乜嘢<br />\n嘩屌 到佢哋&rsquo;表演&rsquo;嗰陣 <br />\n一路梳一路聞到佢哋陣頭油味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好撚臭<br />\n依啲表演真係得支那先諗到<br />\n表演圖慎入<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"109fea5215d65b6cd656451e5a784fbe6998ee87","tid":2068560,"uid":142854,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:01:48.000Z","msg":"我去過長毛象邨<br />\n<br />\n入面男廁d尿兜d毛吉到我好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bce885a88efddb52a6af6005ae7d2522d376ef30","tid":2068560,"uid":37246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:02:56.000Z","msg":"諗起唔知邊到有個部落會將動物嘅屎gel頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94edfa906b6b92eab78e7f6ca6f2091bab58065a","tid":2068560,"uid":37246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bce885a88efddb52a6af6005ae7d2522d376ef30","tid":2068560,"uid":37246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:02:56.000Z","msg":"諗起唔知邊到有個部落會將動物嘅屎gel頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T19:11:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n非洲牛屎Gel<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b782a325c8ab8b0f1f54624550c11025d8bea95b","tid":2068560,"uid":10566,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"94edfa906b6b92eab78e7f6ca6f2091ba